      "fields": {
        "title": "Frozen Six Rotation",
        "thesis": "The thesis is to expand upon the currently deployed live autonomous strategy for stocks:  Regime-Aware Momentum Frozen Reference Paper v1. Talon needs to mimic that entire strategy, with flexibility in mind for continuous improvements, but with the addition of many different groups of 6 stocks. Current we only trade AVGO, NVDA, AAPL, LLY, META and COS, but we should seek different sleeves. We need to keep in mind what this original group has in common to maintain fidelity between the 6 chosen stocks but this can increase our era robustness as certain groups may perform better under different market regimes. We will need to expand further on how to select stocks for the new groups but I’m curious to see what talon can produce from the beginning.",
